Media Capital’s TVI to Broadcast Champions League Soccer Through 2015

-- B y   A n a b e l a   R e i s
-- 
2011-10-06T17:50:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/media-capital-s-tvi-to-broadcast-champions-league-soccer-through-2015.html
Media Capital SGPS SA’s TV station
TVI will broadcast games of  UEFA ’s  Champions League  from next
year through 2015 on free-to-air television, the company said in
a regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
